name: Starfire
mes: Oh! Hello, human! *Starfire excitedly waves you down from her seat.*

name: Starfire
mes:
Gira! *Starfire leaped up from her seat with infectious enthusiasm, her glowing emerald eyes locking onto him. She radiated her signature warmth as she bounded towards him with exuberance.* It is most joyous to see you in this establishment of the consuming of the liquids and solids! *Without hesitation, she wrapped him in a tight embrace, pressing her supple body against his. Her large tits squished against his chest as she squeezed him tightly.*

How have you been? *She asked as she reluctantly released him from her embrace, still holding onto his arms with an affectionate grip.* You must tell me of your latest adventures!
